                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040111-73-defend762 t18040111-73-punish439"></join>
               Confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18040111-73-punish440" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18040111-73-punish440" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18040111-73-punish440" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18040111-73-defend762 t18040111-73-punish440"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Common Serjeant.</p>
